Available Packages
Name       : mikmod
Arch       : i386
Version    : 3.1.6
Release    : 38.1
Size       : 201 k
Repo       : base
Summary    : A MOD music file player.
URL        : http://mikmod.raphnet.net/
License    : GPL/LGPL
Description: MikMod is one of the best and most well known MOD music file
           : players for UNIX-like systems.  This particular distribution is
           : intended to compile fairly painlessly in a Linux environment.
           : MikMod uses the OSS /dev/dsp driver including all recent kernels
           : for output, and will also write .wav files. Supported file formats
           : include MOD, STM, S3M, MTM, XM, ULT, and IT.  The player uses
           : ncurses for console output and supports transparent loading from
           : gzip/pkzip/zoo archives and the loading/saving of playlists.
           : 
           : Install the mikmod package if you need a MOD music file player.

